{"tid":1758994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有三千五百人仲未踢保！！！","createTime":"2019-11-27T11:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T06:26:28.000Z","uid":199926,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b21203cc3e37b032d0c3a8e3316975844853f23e","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"警方6月至今拘捕4319人　<br />\n<br />\n保安局回覆立法會，表示自6月至本月中拘捕4319人，有3508人保釋候查中，644人的案件正在司法程序，167人無條件獲釋，至於涉及禁蒙面法的被捕人數有629人，被起訴有95人。<br />\n<br />\n得咁少人無條件釋放(拒保)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個3508人可以考慮踢保 重獲自由身！<br />\n唔洗報到驚保䆁期間再犯！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mbMLxMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmbMLxMt.png&h=ed6cafc1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acdb5f159aeaa7300121a596fcd0b9ce78de9b42","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:37:43.000Z","msg":"希望多啲手足重新上線香城online<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其是長時間未被起訴 <br />\n非控告嚴重罪行 例如控告非法集結 公眾地方行為不檢嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n雖然踢咗保狗都可以重新拉你 但保䆁期間再犯有機會還押 唔好冒呢個險"},{"pid":"aaa678a9190c622272347794a5c31a5dee6a2199","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:38:50.000Z","msg":"希望嗰三千五百位手足儘快重獲自由身！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86189778f26e3b3dcb288b59b3450bb49df4b9d","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:39:04.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"8f0b39f34bcd483409bc515df1a2e9bedf55e2fe","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:39:58.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"c03ed700a0ca7d10ff9ebc0192b804e5ff8e0cb6","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"25f5555601e41609d575d4adfcf64e69529be5b8","tid":1758994,"uid":199926,"like":0,"